{"tid":2083054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我只有一個願望","createTime":"2020-06-28T13:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T04:27:32.000Z","uid":239492,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"118892b180159528bbb4f9840580cbba7ae40625","tid":2083054,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"我聽日就上庭，後日就裁決。雖然我唔知最後會點，但係我淨係知道7月1號一定要行出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n如果7月1唔企出嚟，可能越嚟越少機會俾我地企出嚟做勢俾外國人睇。就算俾狗打壓香港人嘅遊行自由，我地就係要話俾外國人知，我地香港人仲未放棄，連之鋒同肥佬黎都未放棄！我地都唔可以放棄！<br />\n<br />\n如果有機會，我一定我會同大家齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 建國<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<br />\n我願榮光歸香港🇭🇰<br />\n最後 煲底見"},{"pid":"92bbb5d4e07269376ebacab729ffa12ab6245cba","tid":2083054,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"小推"},{"pid":"49e1edf2c5c768171fe23a7f20019c2820956cba","tid":2083054,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"仆街㩒錯"},{"pid":"584a7f86df50e915f3d9dacd3af6859614e2684f","tid":2083054,"uid":216828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:43:32.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"9665d70023ee78c97d5b3125d46daaa1531aa3de","tid":2083054,"uid":16374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suSqcbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuSqcbf.jpg&h=4ee35773&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51b7401d214599050df7c20179263586f66b5438","tid":2083054,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"一定出"},{"pid":"5ba46f8bb1d5d2b818582c70286694e843104267","tid":2083054,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38ab959e8a24c106713e4529403c553fd7cddc68","tid":2083054,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"71港島見"},{"pid":"5ed13de33418c53e290d6f0